          "thinking": "Now I have all the information I need.\n\nAccording to the current policy:\n1. The expense reimbursement policy (2025 revision) states in Article 5 that the specific amounts are governed by the Authorization Management Method's Appendix 2.\n2. The Authorization Management Method's Appendix 2 (\"费用报销审批权限表\") shows:\n\n| AR-01 | 大于等于0元且小于3000元 | 部门经理 |\n| AR-02 | 大于等于3000元且小于10000元 | 部门经理,并经财务复核 |\n| AR-03 | 大于等于10000元且小于50000元 | 部门总经理 |\n| AR-04 | 大于等于50000元且小于200000元 | 分管副总 |\n| AR-05 | 大于等于200000元 | 总经理办公会 |\n\nSo the answer is: 单笔费用报销达到10000元（含）以上、50000元以下需要部门总经理审批。If the amount reaches 50000元 or more, it needs 分管副总 approval instead.\n\nActually, the question asks \"达到多少金额需要部门总经理审批\". Looking at AR-03, the range is ≥10000元且<50000元. So the minimum amount that requires department general manager approval is 10000元 (含).\n\nThe 2022 deprecated document mentions 8000元, but that's the old policy and has been superseded.\n\nLet me also check the old document for completeness to make sure I'm not missing anything.",
